## Save Flow (`saveMeetingNote()` in NoteDetailView+Actions.swift)
Creates a new `MeetingSession` and appends to `note.meetingSessions`. No string concatenation. State consolidated to single `@State var savedMeetingSessions: [MeetingSession]` in NoteDetailView.

## UI Details
- Session dividers: `HandDrawnDividerLine` Shape (pseudo-random hash, irregular segments)
- `NotesEditor` private wrapper: owns local `@State editableText`, fires `onChanged` callback
- `SessionAccordion`: private inner struct, owns `@State isExpanded` + `@State selectedTab`
- Interactive `MeetingCheckbox` toggles `[ ]`/`[x]` prefix in summary rich text, persists immediately

## Color Token Rule
Both MeetingNoteDetailPanel and AIResultPanel use: `colorScheme == .dark ? Color("DetailPaneColor") : .white`. Do NOT use `SurfaceElevatedColor` for these panels.
